智財法規專論                             SPECIAL ISSUES IN INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY POLICY


  	如何保護個人/產業之智慧財產權，己成為知識創新之全球化競局所探討之焦點。本課程內容涉及著作權法、專利法、商標法、營業秘密法、公平交易法以及技術授權等相關議題，透過案例分析與策略管理觀點進行解析，以使學生對相關智財法規之規範與運用有所瞭解與掌握。Due to the current globalization of knowledge innovations, individual or industrial intellectual property rights have been a popular focus.  The course involves Copyright Act, Patent Act, Trademark Act, Trade Secret, Fair Trade Act, Technology Authorization and other related issues.  The course will serve a practical purpose via case analysis and policy management discussions.

課程教育目標 

A 創意產業跨領域整合研究與人才 Research of interdisciplinary integration and talent incubator in creative industriesB 國際與華人創產研究之學術重鎮與產官學研智庫 The academic hub for international and Chinese in creatiD 創意產業本土理論論述與國際匯流 Theoretical discourse of local creative industries and international convergen 
