課程概述 Course Description
       如何保護個人/產業之智慧財產權，己成為知識創新之全球化競局所探討之焦點。本課程內容涉及著作權法、專利法、商標法、營業秘密法、公平交易法以及技術授權等相關議題，透過案例分析與策略管理觀點進行解析，以使學生對相關智財法規之規範與運用有所瞭解與掌握。Due to the current globalization of knowledge innovations, individual or industrial intellectual property rights have been a popular focus.  The course involves Copyright Act, Patent Act, Trademark Act, Trade Secret, Fair Trade Act, Technology Authorization and other related issues.  The course will serve a practical purpose via case analysis and policy management discussions.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    This course aims to build students’ fundamental understanding of IPR legal system about copyright, trademark, patent, trade secret and antitrust law, thereby developing the analytical capabilities in real IPR issues. The course will also use real corporate cases to discuss different topics in IPR development, especially focusing on the IPR current issues in creative and design industry. Students will learn to analyze the IPR issues from various perspectives based on the course materials in news cases, practical management tools, related research papers, and IP resource planning simulation, thereby cultivating theoretical and practical analytical skills for future IPR studying.

* To build students’ fundamental concept of IPR knowledge and articles of act.
* To develop students’ analyzing capabilities in IPR cases.
* To develop students’ skills of using management tools in IPR practice
* To understand and design a research framework of IPR studies.
* To learn a IPR planning in a new start-up concept.

本課程目的在訓練學生對著作權、商標、專利、營業秘密與公平交易法等智財法規的認識，進而培養對實務智財議題的分析能力，課程中將以實際企業個案探討不同智財主題，並強調創意與設計產業的智財發展現況。課程內容將運用時事個案、智財分析工具操作、相關研究論文、與實際的智財資源規劃模擬，令學生自不同面向理解智財議題全貌，並培養理論與實務的各類分析能力。

* 建立學生對智財知識與法條的基本概念。
* 建立學生對智財實務個案的分析能力。
* 熟悉智財實務中的管理分析工具。
* 暸解並學習設計智財相關研究主題。
* 學習規劃新創公司的智財佈局。
     

